These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Beverage: water, hot-chocolate, sprite, juice
Nationality: chinese, egyptian, thai, turkish
1. Nationality:egyptian is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1
2. Beverage:water == Nationality:turkish##1
3. Nationality:thai is on the right of Nationality:chinese##1
4. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left of Nationality:turkish##1
5. Beverage:juice is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage          | juice | sprite | hot-chocolate | water   |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | chinese     | thai   | turkish |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
Food: eggplant, avocado, cranberry, pear
1. Hobby:woodworking == Food:avocado##1
2. Hobby:camping is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:cooking is on the right of Hobby:woodworking##1
4. Hobby:woodworking is on the right of Food:cranberry##1
5. Food:avocado is on the left of Food:eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Food   | cranberry    | avocado      | eggplant | pear |

