.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
Nationality: american, argentine, mexican, nigerian
Sport: baseball, parkour, surfing, ice-hockey
1. Sport:baseball is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1
2. Sport:parkour is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
3. Nationality:american is on the left of Nationality:mexican##1
4. Nationality:nigerian == Sport:ice-hockey##1
5. Sport:baseball is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Sport     | surfing  | baseball    | parkour       | ice-hockey |

 